creator: SCUBAPRO
descriptionHtml:
SCUBAPRO LogTRAK 2.0 is the mobile dive logbook for Android mobile devices. LogTRAK 2.0 allows you to download and analyze your dive profile data on Android-based mobile phones.
This App is compatible with SCUBAPRO GALILEO HUD, GALILEO 2 (G2), GALILEO 2 CONSOLE (G2C), A-Series (ALADIN SPORT and ALADIN H dive computers) and the Aladin Watch Series A1 and A2. To interface with your dive computer, you’ll need to enable Bluetooth on your Android phone and set your dive computer to BLE READY mode.
LogTRAK 2.0 is the perfect way to view your dives, keep them organized on your mobile device and easily access them wherever you go.

Features:
• Record and manage your dives
• Analyze data like depth, temperature and heart rate profile
• Incorporate additional dive information
• Adjust dive computer settings from your phone
• Update dive computer software and firmware from your phone
descriptionShort: Download dive logs from your SCUBAPRO dive computer and analyze them.
